high_descs: Turn to the right and cross to stand to the right of the toilet facing the towel.
Pick the soap up from the back of the toilet.
Turn around to face the tub.
Put the soap into the tub.
Move to the left and turn to face the tub.
Pick the soap up from the ledge of the tub.
Move over to the right side of the tub.
Put the soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around and go to tub.  Turn around and move until standing between tub and toilet.
Lift up pink bar of soap from back of toilet, located next to the toilet paper.
Turn around and move to the side until facing the tub.
Put pink soap in tub, between the purple cloths, but closer to the one on the right, near the outer tub wall.
Turn and place self in front of bar of soap on the side of the tub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap from the side of the tub.
Move to your right until positioned in front of the soap that was placed inside the tub.
Place the second bar of soap to the left of the other bar of soap inside the tub.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of pink soap into a tub.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the toilet
pick up soap from the toilet
move to the center of the tub behind you
put the soap in the tub
Move to the right side of the toilet facing the tub
pick up soap from the rub
move to the center of the tub ahead of you
put the soap in the tub
anns.task_desc: Put two bars of soap in the tub.
